title: Ken Jennings
summary: Kenneth Wayne Jennings III[1] (born May 23, 1974) is an American game show contestant and host, author, and television presenter. He is the highest-earning American game show contestant, having won money on five different games shows, including $4,522,700 on Jeopardy!. Jennings currently hosts Jeopardy!, sharing duties with Mayim Bialik.[2]
